{"tid":2349430,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"傳李嘉誠淡出AlipayHK　有意收購英國最大長租公寓項目","createTime":"2021-01-01T14:25:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-02T02:21:02.000Z","uid":362199,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"2670e9e35cbd6c3908f6974fd65e346c8fe0e4d9","tid":2349430,"uid":362199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T14:25:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/htm/hk-alipay-11232020035727.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fcantonese%2Fnews%2Fhtm%2Fhk-alipay-11232020035727.html&d=3ylU62tgaeYkhBfBjxJ1gXXW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=78b0a293\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/htm/hk-alipay-11232020035727.html</a><br />\n<br />\n香港《蘋果日報》報道，一度在香港作為AlipayHK「引路人」角色的長和，本身與阿里旗下螞蟻集團各佔50%股權，平分秋色，但現在兩間公司的合資企業換血，長期追隨李嘉誠的霍建寧等人辭任董事，僅餘下一位長和代表，同時長和持股下降至四成左右，失去最終決策權。<br />\n<br />\n而同時，有消息指李嘉誠正在支持收購英國最大的長租公寓項目&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;倫敦溫布利公園（Wembley Park）地塊，該項目價值估計高達30億英鎊。<br />\n<br />\n就AlipayHK的變動，《蘋果》報道引述AlipayHK回應指舉動屬「提升營運效率」。分析指，螞蟻取回AlipayHK是取回主導權，不排除未來增加合作夥伴。<br />\n<br />\n長和與螞蟻於2017年合資成立Alipay Payment Services(HK)（下稱AlipayHK），在香港共同營運電子錢包支付寶香港，拓展香港電子支付市場。翻查資料，AlipayHK由CKHH Alipay Internet Services(HK)（下稱CKHH Alipay）全資擁有，其中長和及螞蟻分別透過旗下公司Rossinant以及Antfin(HK)Holding（下稱Antfin），多次共同「對等注資」CKHH Alipay，各持有9,634.2萬股份，涉及金額達1.93億美元（約15.1億港元），兩大集團各持50%股權。<br />\n<br />\n直至今年9月，CKHH Alipay再度增發股份，惟有別以前，此次只向螞蟻旗下的Antfin配發，涉及4,970.9萬股（涉6,200萬美元），完成後螞蟻持股躍升至60.3%，長和則攤薄至僅39.7%。<br />\n<br />\nAlipayHK原本董事局長和及螞蟻雙方各有2名董事代表，過去數年仍然維持勢均力敵比例，惟配發股份同日，董事局出現人事變動，長和老臣子及螞蟻高層全數離任董事一職，包括長和聯席董事總經理霍建寧、副董事總經理陸法蘭，以及螞蟻集團高級副總裁Douglas Feagin、首席財務官韓歆毅。<br />\n<br />\n大換血後，董事局重新任命3名新成員，包括螞蟻金服國際投資主管萬啓年、螞蟻集團國際事業群總裁趙穎，以及現時是AlipayHK CEO、曾出任和記電訊營運總裁陳婉真作為代表，螞蟻一共佔2席，長和僅得1席，變相螞蟻獲得終極決策權。<br />\n<br />\nAlipayHK發言人代表螞蟻及長和回應指稱，是次變動是雙方進一步提升AlipayHK營運效率而共同作出的決定，是次股份增持也是螞蟻一直看好香港發展前景而作出的具體行動，希望能更好地支持其業務發展和服務香港市民。<br />\n<br />\n另外，英國媒體近日報道指李嘉誠支持的Long Harbour正在競購英國最大的長租公寓項目倫敦溫布利公園地塊。<br />\n<br />\n長實方面周一（23日）對報道低調回應。長實相關人士指，Long Harbour曾於數十年前與長實集團共同發展一個地產項目，長實集團僅持有其少數股權，並沒有參與其董事會或日常管理的套論及決策。"},{"pid":"278368c82a91d985699ed49f37eb81e5b82b3ecd","tid":2349430,"uid":222140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T14:26:17.000Z","msg":"搞地產最穩陣"},{"pid":"2c35bbfd2c6bcd061abb324780f3c11ed4ddf5d0","tid":2349430,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T14:26:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44e9639163eb0585cd3b3f11ec4a55d5f079964d","tid":2349430,"uid":138964,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T14:28:47.000Z","msg":"香港人逃唔出誠仔魔掌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a0bb9c0156d19b58170286c491bb882473f9297","tid":2349430,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"278368c82a91d985699ed49f37eb81e5b82b3ecd","tid":2349430,"uid":222140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T14:26:17.000Z","msg":"搞地產最穩陣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T14:29:02.000Z","msg":"英國地產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nnot香港地產"},{"pid":"b0f6283c5767733d6752638ccb7b4bde07f8b3b4","tid":2349430,"uid":347237,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T14:29:04.000Z","msg":"alipay hk 用戶信息直接送中"},{"pid":"1df90c47a8d7b319482263f6179c0920b469e056","tid":2349430,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44e9639163eb0585cd3b3f11ec4a55d5f079964d","tid":2349430,"uid":138964,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T14:28:47.000Z","msg":"香港人逃唔出誠仔魔掌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T14:29:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ef38d36aa9be250091f84d075c3790ab040914f","tid":2349430,"uid":32675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T14:30:07.000Z","msg":"移民英國都脫離唔到誠仔既魔爪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"647346949f6b615b54c569020249b3e94f92f16f","tid":2349430,"uid":18251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T14:31:16.000Z","msg":"嚟緊alipayhk應該死得比大陸劏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dbadd92bf39d753d296c7b3c1ae7c2ed6ef7229","tid":2349430,"uid":22535,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2ef38d36aa9be250091f84d075c3790ab040914f","tid":2349430,"uid":32675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T14:30:07.000Z","msg":"移民英國都脫離唔到誠仔既魔爪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T14:45:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幫誠仔打工，都好過做支共狗菜"},{"pid":"9cdcee39029f1e7aaddab9740b0567214f22c046","tid":2349430,"uid":182519,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T14:47:03.000Z","msg":"跟誠哥行實無死"},{"pid":"c546409d20c053addad6f2ae8ddd1a9334950601","tid":2349430,"uid":138964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4dbadd92bf39d753d296c7b3c1ae7c2ed6ef7229","tid":2349430,"uid":22535,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2ef38d36aa9be250091f84d075c3790ab040914f","tid":2349430,"uid":32675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T14:30:07.000Z","msg":"移民英國都脫離唔到誠仔既魔爪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T14:45:22.0