買英國</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f0b69a261ceb9588c6fb803ff59ef3ee502be1f","tid":2349430,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5a0bb9c0156d19b58170286c491bb882473f9297","tid":2349430,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"278368c82a91d985699ed49f37eb81e5b82b3ecd","tid":2349430,"uid":222140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T14:26:17.000Z","msg":"搞地產最穩陣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T14:29:02.000Z","msg":"英國地產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nnot香港地產"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T15:34:17.000Z","msg":"李嘉誠好重視法律是否保護資產<br />\n<br />\n佢都睇到香港法治玩完"},{"pid":"a77b42d2a871974a3b0fd4548e7c95464b3d233c","tid":2349430,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T15:37:20.000Z","msg":"你地真係唔跟誠哥走？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f48bc1c2f11967f34ec791242d3b350575d6ec03","tid":2349430,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T16:15:11.000Z","msg":"好先進<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a2286c261fb3665cef38cd8ec942db63faeb87a","tid":2349430,"uid":34222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T16:17:56.000Z","msg":"去到英國都要幫誠哥打工<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50b9308ff93277558d08a093e84d67aae225f55f","tid":2349430,"uid":293494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2670e9e35cbd6c3908f6974fd65e346c8fe0e4d9","tid":2349430,"uid":362199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T14:25:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/htm/hk-alipay-11232020035727.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fcantonese%2Fnews%2Fhtm%2Fhk-alipay-11232020035727.html&d=3ylU62tgaeYkhBfBjxJ1gXXW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=78b0a293\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/htm/hk-alipay-11232020035727.html</a><br />\n<br />\n香港《蘋果日報》報道，一度在香港作為AlipayHK「引路人」角色的長和，本身與阿里旗下螞蟻集團各佔50%股權，平分秋色，但現在兩間公司的合資企業換血，長期追隨李嘉誠的霍建寧等人辭任董事，僅餘下一位長和代表，同時長和持股下降至四成左右，失去最終決策權。<br />\n<br />\n而同時，有消息指李嘉誠正在支持收購英國最大的長租公寓項目&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;倫敦溫布利公園（Wembley Park）地塊，該項目價值估計高達30億英鎊。<br />\n<br />\n就AlipayHK的變動，《蘋果》報道引述AlipayHK回應指舉動屬「提升營運效率」。分析指，螞蟻取回AlipayHK是取回主導權，不排除未來增加合作夥伴。<br />\n<br />\n長和與螞蟻於2017年合資成立Alipay Payment Services(HK)（下稱AlipayHK），在香港共同營運電子錢包支付寶香港，拓展香港電子支付市場。翻查資料，AlipayHK由CKHH Alipay Internet Services(HK)（下稱CKHH Alipay）全資擁有，其中長和及螞蟻分別透過旗下公司Rossinant以及Antfin(HK)Holding（下稱Antfin），多次共同「對等注資」CKHH Alipay，各持有9,634.2萬股份，涉及金額達1.93億美元（約15.1億港元），兩大集團各持50%股權。<br />\n<br />\n直至今年9月，CKHH Alipay再度增發股份，惟有別以前，此次只向螞蟻旗下的Antfin配發，涉及4,970.9萬股（涉6,200萬美元），完成後螞蟻持股躍升至60.3%，長和則攤薄至僅39.7%。<br />\n<br />\nAlipayHK原本董事局長和及螞蟻雙方各有2名董事代表，過去數年仍然維持勢均力敵比例，惟配發股份同日，董事局出現人事變動，長和老臣子及螞蟻高層全數離任董事一職，包括長和聯席董事總經理霍建寧、副董事總經理陸法蘭，以及螞蟻集團高級副總裁Douglas Feagin、首席財務官韓歆毅。<br />\n<br />\n大換血後，董事局重新任命3名新成員，包括螞蟻金服國際投資主管萬啓年、螞蟻集團國際事業群總裁趙穎，以及現時是AlipayHK CEO、曾出任和記電訊營運總裁陳婉真作為代表，螞蟻一共佔2席，長和僅得1席，變相螞蟻獲得終極決策權。<br />\n<br />\nAlipayHK發言人代表螞蟻及長和回應指稱，是次變動是雙方進一步提升AlipayHK營運效率而共同作出的決定，是次股份增持也是螞蟻一直看好香港發展前景而作出的具體行動，希望能更好地支持其業務發展和服務香港市民。<br />\n<br />\n另外，英國媒體近日報道指李嘉誠支持的Long Harbour正在競購英國最大的長租公寓項目倫敦溫布利公園地塊。<br />\n<br />\n長實方面周一（23日）對報道低調回應。長實相關人士指，Long Harbour曾於數十年前與長實集團共同發展一個地產項目，長實集團僅持有其少數股權，並沒有參與其董事會或日常管理的套論及決策。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T16:20:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ubREMPO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FubREMPO.png&h=b6b462e2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"12bc27ff84d0e2ce419c2599526587de366ee93b","tid":2349430,"uid":19012,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T16:21:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ww9Snos.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fww9Snos.jpg&h=1b6c8cf4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"02e559cfe623b6b9e2bd32822af230c79c00ebfc","tid":2349430,"uid":51754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T16:22:26.000Z","msg":"[求推] 衞生署 強制檢測名單 又双叒叕有錯？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2349363\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2349363</a>"},{"pid":"1231434b023521ba524306a79085a54a72beae18","tid":2349430,"uid":47198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T16:27:10.000Z","msg":"11月23號 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}